full_title: I Am Not Okay by Jelly Roll
title: I Am Not Okay

description.plain: First performed pre-release at Jelly Roll’s first CMA Fest (2024), “I Am Not Okay” explores themes of mental health and emphasizes the importance of knowing that “it’s okay to not be okay.” Jelly Roll’s vulnerability creates strong emotions evident in the manner of his singing.
